Let us earn your trust and be you Roofers Grand Lake OK!
We will always give you 5 star service, workmanship, and materials that exceed your expectations!
​
We realize that selecting a roofing contractor can be a very difficult process. Here at ACC roofing, we promise to make that process a breeze.
We treat your home like it belonged to our family. We want our customers to have the highest quality and value for their roofing and restoration needs.
That means we spend extra time during inspections, use the highest quality roofing materials, and use the best crews that are certified by the manufacturers so you get the best warranty possible! We are storm damage restoration specialists with 30+ years of experience.
CONTACT US & LET US HELP YOU NOW. WE WILL ANSWER ALL YOUR QUESTIONS
AND GUIDE YOU WITHOUT ANY PRESSURE!

Our Services
CALL (918) 910-ROOF (7663)
New Roof Replacement
Our commitment to quality is second to none. Our in-house crews have been working with us for 20 years and we never had one of our roofs leak!
Commercial Roofing Specialists
We proudly serve Oklahoma businesses with replacement, repairs, coatings, and maintenance. We are highly trained in the newest commercial roofing innovations. We specialize in TPO, Modified Bitumen, and Standing Seam Metal.
Roof Repairs
Fast, efficient, and affordable repair is how we have built our reputation. We only use the best crews who are certified by the manufacturers for the best warranty possible.
Quality Roof Inspections
ACC Roofing provides the most comprehensive roof inspections in Oklahoma. Our decades of experience and expertise is combined with drone and thermal imaging for extremely safe and accurate roof inspections.
Skylight Repair & Replace
ACC Roofing is a full service roofing company that can handle all of your roofing construction needs including expert skylight installations and repairs.
Emergency Repair & Tarp Down
ACC Roofing is here for you 24/7 when damaging storms leave your home exposed. ACC crews can quickly help protect your home and furnishings from more extensive damage if your roof has been compromised in any way.

FAQ
Should I repair or replace my roof?
We will gladly perform the inspection and give you our professional recommendations. A repair may be all you need or may buy some time before your roof needs to be replaced. We will provide an honest assessment and never pressure you into doing more than you need.
How long does a roof replacement take?
Most roofs are completed in 1 day for minimal disruption to your schedule. Larger projects and some specialty systems usually require more time.
What roofing options do you offer?
Clay and Concrete Tile, Natural and Synthetic Slate, Metal shake, Stone Coated Steel, Standing Seam Metal, Composition Shingles, TPO, Modified Bitumen etc.
